**Summary:**

This is a fork of [this mod](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/daylight-mobs/) which stops mobs from burning in the daylight (This can be disabled in the config) and allows hostile mobs to spawn during the day (This is disabled by default and can be enabled in the config).
